關稅理論與實務














 
關稅理論與實務
 









科目名稱 : 關稅理論與實務
開課班級 : 日國貿四合
學　　分 : 2.00
授課時數 : 2


授課教師 : 趙繼祖
科目英文名稱 : Theory and Practice of Customs Tax
 










教學目標(中文)


OBJECTIVES：
Customs operations form one of the important elements of international trade. Students taking this course are expected to familiarize themselves with the following two aspects：First, they realize the customs operations in the course of importation and exportation. Second, they are able to use the customs measures to promote their businesses. Since our economy is export-oriented, this courses will include, besides government laws regulating the importation and exportation, actual practices in calculating the costs of imported goods and bonding and refund operations.










教學目標(英文)


 










成績評定


平時40%,期中30%,期末30%
點名不到次數上限為不得超過3次
平時測驗3次










